&lt;p&gt;（2）也可以去 GitHub 上下：&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2RvY2tlci9jb21wb3NlL3JlbGVhc2Vz&#34;&gt;https://github.com/docker/compose/releases&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
